# Nx
.nx/

# SSL certs — local-only, never committed.
# `certs/` is the legacy pre-`infra/` location; keep it in the ignore
# set so a habit-`mkcert -key-file certs/...` can't accidentally
# commit a private key after the move. `scripts/migrate-local-certs.mjs`
# walks any existing files into `infra/certs/` on the next `pnpm dev:up`.
certs/
infra/certs/*
!infra/certs/README.md
apps/web/certificates/
# Defense-in-depth catch-all for stray TLS material anywhere in the tree.
**/*.pem
**/*-key.pem

# Brainstorming companion server (Superpowers skill)
.superpowers/

# One-off scratch outputs (venue-photo comparison, etc.)
tmp/
